Step By Step

Create folder 
  - pages
  - components
  
ionic generate page index
ionic generate page home

ionic generate page pages/welcome
ionic generate page pages/login
ionic generate page pages/signup
ionic generate page pages/feed
ionic generate page pages/messages
ionic generate page pages/notification
ionic generate page pages/settings

ionic generate module components

ionic generate component components/logo
ionic generate component components/slides
ionic generate component components/start

components.module.ts
  declarations: [SlidesComponent],
  exports: [SlidesComponent],

npm run build

ionic capacitor add ios
ionic capacitor add android


Status Bar
  ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-statusbar
  npm install @ionic-native/status-bar
  
  tambahkan app.components.ts
  this.statusBar.overlaysWebView(true);
  this.statusBar.backgroundColorByHexString('#33000000');